data.title: Marines TV
data.meta_description:
Today, the U.S. Navy christened its newest guided-missile destroyer in honor of the first African-American Marine aviator, Lt. Gen. Frank E. Petersen, Jr.

(U.S. Marine Corps video by Cpl. Shannon Doherty)

For a descriptive transcript text document of this production, contact Kim Hardison at Kimberly.hardison@usmc.mil.
